{"tid":1887941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良：政府領導層「未醒」 稱疫情受控是混淆視聽","createTime":"2020-02-20T01:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T03:05:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"12472a5f80a398785e5ee91ba976991827152335","tid":1887941,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:52:45.000Z","msg":"何栢良：本港疫情受控的說法大錯特錯<br />\n<br />\n香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，在本台節目表示，新型冠狀病毒疫情在本港一定未受控，甚至擔心會失控。他解釋說，起碼要在一個潛伏期，即是至少14天內無新增感染個案，疫情才算是受控，批評政務司長張建宗指疫情受控，是混淆視聽、大錯特錯，呼籲對方直接承認說法有誤。何栢良質疑，政府領導層「未醒」，指本港出現首宗確診個案後，當局仍然未啟用相關超級電腦，追蹤患者的密切接觸者，是令人震驚，形容政府「日日等病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265435&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1265435%26csid%3D261_341&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5OaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=e4e398f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265435&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6c15ccdba94007ef6f447218959f35321d310de7","tid":1887941,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻，第一日知正苦班仆街好想冚港剷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f3b2defb3804bef88047f05a1157bb789506f5","tid":1887941,"uid":199907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"大陸話受控你話未受控？"},{"pid":"63a6b90d721bf1b4a9b9de661feeaf70140e264a","tid":1887941,"uid":255624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1821235d86ff0af01286e3ef82b09e2fe6d141","tid":1887941,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"@張建宗"},{"pid":"05b10b08aeb97ab27f193ddb7b8e3e14857cf382","tid":1887941,"uid":64743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":